      <head>Ludwig Scheibler (1848-1921)</head>
      <div>
        <!-- BODY: -->
        <p><hi rend="bold">Ludwig Scheibler (1848-1921),</hi> art historian and music historian.  Among his publications was <hi rend="italic">Geschichte der K&#xF6;lner Malerschule</hi> (1894-1902).</p>
        <p>Scheibler published a monograph on <hi rend="italic">Franz Schuberts einstimmige Lieder, Ges&#xE4;nge, und Balladen mit Texten von Schiller</hi> in 1905.  Together with Otto Erich Deutsch, Scheibler was one of the key figures in early Schubert scholarship.</p>
        <p>There is no known correspondence between Scheibler and Schenker.  His name arises in correspondence with Otto Erich Deutsch.</p>
        <p><hi rend="italic">Contributor:</hi>  Christoph Hust</p>
